---
title: Seared Lemon-Pepper Beef with Roast Potatoes & Mustard Veggies
description: The trick to making your veggie sides as good as the main event? Just give them a little TLC! With a few classic flavours, this broccoli and carrot more than holds its own with succulent lemon pepper beef.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c3e7e30c445fa29e21425b2-b0f17f68.jpg
